00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.000
вЂЄDon't insult me.

402
00:20:33.083 --> 00:20:34.458
вЂЄI'm insulting you?

403
00:20:53.208 --> 00:20:55.416
вЂЄI want you to return Mpume's phone.

404
00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:57.791
вЂЄBut Ma. I don't know
вЂЄwhere Mpume's phone is. though.

405
00:20:57.875 --> 00:20:58.875
вЂЄSarah.

406
00:21:04.125 --> 00:21:05.125
вЂЄLook at me.

407
00:21:07.750 --> 00:21:09.125
вЂЄ[exhales sharply]

408
00:21:18.500 --> 00:21:20.291
вЂЄ[gqom music playing on headphones]

409
00:21:20.375 --> 00:21:21.375
вЂЄ[clears throat]

410
00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.583
вЂЄ[Jonasi] Listen here. boy.

411
00:21:27.666 --> 00:21:28.666
вЂЄ[music stops]

412
00:21:29.375 --> 00:21:30.791
вЂЄWhy did youвЂ¦

413
00:21:31.791 --> 00:21:35.916
вЂЄlet Mpume and her friends
вЂЄturn my house into a madhouse?

414
00:21:36.666 --> 00:21:37.958
вЂЄ[Joyce] Jonasi.

415
00:21:38.041 --> 00:21:40.583
вЂЄ-I thought we already spoke about this?
вЂЄ-No. love.

416
00:21:41.666 --> 00:21:43.333
вЂЄI want Menzi to answer.

417
00:21:45.458 --> 00:21:49.958
вЂЄ[stammering] Yes. Dad.
вЂЄI tried to stop them. You can ask Mpume.

418
00:21:50.041 --> 00:21:52.041
вЂЄ-Mpume!
вЂЄ-[Jonasi] I'm asking you.

419
00:21:52.625 --> 00:21:54.375
вЂЄYou're the firstborn son.

420
00:21:54.458 --> 00:21:58.958
вЂЄSo why are you acting weak
вЂЄwhen you're my son?

421
00:21:59.041 --> 00:22:01.416
вЂЄYou haven't been the man
вЂЄof this house for the entire year.

422
00:22:01.500 --> 00:22:02.916
вЂЄAt least Menzi's trying.

423
00:22:03.416 --> 00:22:05.125
вЂЄ[suspenseful music playing]

424
00:22:05.208 --> 00:22:06.208
вЂЄExcuse me?

425
00:22:08.791 --> 00:22:10.166
вЂЄWhat did you say to me?

426
00:22:11.500 --> 00:22:12.791
вЂЄMy love.

427
00:22:12.875 --> 00:22:15.583
вЂЄ-Who do you think you're talking to?
вЂЄ-Oh. you want to be a father now?

428
00:22:15.666 --> 00:22:16.958
вЂЄYou walked out on us. Dad.

429
00:22:17.041 --> 00:22:18.333
вЂЄHave you forgotten?

430
00:22:21.208 --> 00:22:22.208
вЂЄ[scoffs]

431
00:22:34.875 --> 00:22:36.458
вЂЄHmm. [sniffles]

432
00:22:37.666 --> 00:22:39.208
вЂЄ[sighs] I've seen it all.

433
00:22:40.458 --> 00:22:41.458
вЂЄ[exhales sharply]

434
00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:44.583
вЂЄHow the mighty have fallen.

435
00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:47.750
вЂЄ[scoffs]

436
00:22:53.833 --> 00:22:55.541
вЂЄ-[glass shatters]
вЂЄ-[Joyce] Jo!

437
00:22:55.625 --> 00:22:57.166
вЂЄ[dramatic music playing]

438
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.250
вЂЄDon't you ever talk to me like that.
вЂЄUnderstood?

439
00:22:59.333 --> 00:23:00.333
вЂЄJonasi.

440
00:23:00.416 --> 00:23:02.000
вЂЄ[Jonasi] I'm not one of your buddies!

441
00:23:02.583 --> 00:23:04.125
вЂЄDo you hear me. Mpume?

442
00:23:08.541 --> 00:23:11.166
вЂЄYou. stop being a weakling.

443
00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:13.708
вЂЄToughen up.

444
00:23:14.583 --> 00:23:15.875
вЂЄ-Stand up when I'm talking to you!
вЂЄ-Stop!

445
00:23:15.958 --> 00:23:18.000
вЂЄ-Stop being weak!
вЂЄ-Leave him alone!

446
00:23:18.083 --> 00:23:19.875
вЂЄ[distorted clamoring]

447
00:23:20.541 --> 00:23:21.833
вЂЄYou're hurting him!

448
00:23:21.916 --> 00:23:24.375
вЂЄ-Jonasi. stop!
вЂЄ-[breathing heavily]

449
00:23:26.166 --> 00:23:28.208
вЂЄ[Mpume] Do you really wanna kill him?

450
00:23:30.916 --> 00:23:32.166
вЂЄ-[coughing]
вЂЄ-Menzi. are you okay?

451
00:23:33.125 --> 00:23:34.250
вЂЄAre you okay. bro?

452
00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:38.000
вЂЄ-[door slams]
вЂЄ-[Menzi breathing heavily]

453
00:23:38.083 --> 00:23:39.666
вЂЄIt's going to be okay.

454
00:23:40.916 --> 00:23:41.916
вЂЄIt's okay.

455
00:23:42.416 --> 00:23:45.083
вЂЄ[both sobbing]

456
00:23:47.875 --> 00:23:49.208
вЂЄIt's okay.

457
00:23:50.458 --> 00:23:53.875
вЂЄ-[sobbing continues]
вЂЄ-It's okay. my boy.

458
